		<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.elmorsa.pe/2011/08/11/dafne-plou-mujeres-tecnologia-y-poder/"><![CDATA[<div class="tweetmeme_button" style="float: right; margin-left: 10px;">
			<a href="http://api.tweetmeme.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.elmorsa.pe%2F2011%2F08%2F11%2Fdafne-plou-mujeres-tecnologia-y-poder%2F"><br />
				<img src="http://api.tweetmeme.com/imagebutton.gif?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.elmorsa.pe%2F2011%2F08%2F11%2Fdafne-plou-mujeres-tecnologia-y-poder%2F&amp;source=elmorsa&amp;style=normal&amp;b=2" height="61" width="50" /><br />
